import React from 'react'; import './SimpleTable.css'; const SimpleTable = ({ trades }) => { const formatValue = (value, type = 'default') => { if (value === null || value === undefined) return '-'; switch (type) { case 'currency': return typeof value === 'number' ? `$${value.toFixed(value < 1 ? 6 : 2)}` : value; case 'percentage': return typeof value === 'number' ? `${value.toFixed(2)}%` : value; default: return typeof value === 'number' ? value.toFixed(2) : value; } }; return (
{trades.map((trade, index) => ( ))}
Status Token Price Setup Conf% TF P&L Entry Target Stop R:R Time MW Band EMA34 SMA21 MFI ADX DI+/- Volume Korean BTC% Fund% Social Whale
{trade.status} {trade.token} {formatValue(trade.price, 'currency')} {trade.setupType} {trade.confidence}% {trade.timeframe} {formatValue(trade.unrealizedPnl, 'percentage')} {formatValue(trade.entryPrice, 'currency')} {formatValue(trade.target1, 'currency')} {formatValue(trade.stopLoss, 'currency')} {trade.riskReward}:1 {trade.timeRemaining} {trade.mwIndicators?.mwBandPosition || '-'} {formatValue(trade.mwIndicators?.ema34, 'currency')} {formatValue(trade.mwIndicators?.sma21, 'currency')} {formatValue(trade.mwIndicators?.mfi)} {formatValue(trade.mwIndicators?.adx)} {formatValue(trade.mwIndicators?.diPlus)}/{formatValue(trade.mwIndicators?.diMinus)} {trade.mwIndicators?.volume24h || '-'} {trade.mwIndicators?.koreanInfluence || '-'} {formatValue(trade.mwIndicators?.btcCorrelation * 100)} {formatValue(trade.mwIndicators?.funding, 'percentage')} {formatValue(trade.mwIndicators?.socialSentiment)} {trade.mwIndicators?.whaleActivity || '-'}
); }; export default SimpleTable;
